# The selected BGE embedding model is NOT tracked in git (the ~110MB ONNX file exceeds
# GitHub's 100MB-per-file limit). It lives under public/models/bge-base-en-v1.5/ locally
# and is downloaded by `npm run eval:fetch-model`. The prebuild SHA-256-verifies it.
